    "text": [
        "Dear Maam,",
        "I,Myra Arora ,student of class XII A of your school.I am writing this letter to inform you about my failure to return my library books on time. I have got two books for physics and chemistry respectively and they are issued till 14th August.",
        "Actually,I had to visit my grandfather urgently as he fell down from the stairs and got his leg injured.He will be having  bone plating surgery and it will take one month to recover .As there is no one to look after him,so I along with my parents will remain there till he gets well.",
        "Furthermore, I will be able to return the books after 20 August as my cousin is coming to our home and he can return the books at the school reception .",
        "Please accept my sincere apologies for the delay  as it is unintentional. Moreover,I can also deposit the fine for the late submission of books .",
        "yours faithfully,",
        "Myra"
